                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَٱلۡحِكۡمَةِ﴾: السُّنَّةِ النَّبَويَّةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "35": {
